flowchart TB
    SLACK{WNS sign?}
    SLACK -->|positive| MEET[Path meets timing<br/>increase depth or freq<br/>until WNS approaches zero]
    SLACK -->|near zero| LIMIT[At the technology's<br/>budget for this shape<br/>--> publish this point]
    SLACK -->|negative| BUDGET[Path misses by abs WNS ns<br/>--> marginal cost of this depth]
    MEET --> SWEEP[Sweep next parameter point]
    LIMIT --> SWEEP
    BUDGET --> SWEEP
